org.apache.ctakes.temporal.utils

Enum TlinkType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TlinkType>
      • org.apache.ctakes.temporal.utils.TlinkType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<TlinkType>

    public enum TlinkType
extends Enum<TlinkType>
    Enumeration of the three temporal relation types used in THYME (before, overlap, contains) and their reciprocals (after, overlap, contained_by) Begins-on and Ends-on added 4-11-2013
